    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hello, Molly! I just made these last night for the first time. I&#8217;m not much of a cilantro fan, so I chopped up some fresh basil instead. They&#8217;re divine! I think i <>under<>worked the meat, actually, because I kept losing pine nuts in the pan and having to fish them out before they burned. (Mmm, pine nuts.) I&#8217;m considering whether it would work to slide them into the oven on a baking sheet. What do you think?</p>
<p>Either way, thank you for another fabulous recipe!</p>
    </div>

